- Add a static function `clear_freelist(ProfilerObject *pObj)` with the above code.
- Call `clear_freelist(self);` after `flush_unmatched(self);` in `profiler_disable`.
- Call `clear_freelist(op);` after `flush_unmatched(op);` in `profiler_dealloc`.

